"fai clic su tutte le frecce :guilabel:`> (frecce a destra)` per visualizzare"
" tutti i campi. "

#: ../../content/applications/essentials/export_import_data.rst:53
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`+ (plus sign)` icon button is present to add fields to the "
